{"_id":"4BRyOG1nnNOOkOhN","name":"觀星者 Vizier","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Vizier.png\" width=\"181\" height=\"244\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>真相，就藏在那滿天的星斗之中</em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>抽出這張卡片後一年的任一時間，你可以在冥想時向宇宙詢問1個問題，而DM有義務誠實回答。</p>\n<p>你可以問任何問題，而宇宙必須回答你，答案必定真實，但有可能晦澀難懂。 </p>\n</section>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Vizier.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_hz58kjjjx1","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Many Things","color":"#6b5988"}}}
