{"_id":"4hSNHhWCZN5p5jsE","name":"布蘭多布里斯的披風 Coat of Brandobaris","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/008_-__E9_AD_94_E6_B3_95_E7_89_A9_E5_93_81/001_-__E5_B8_83_E8_98_AD_E5_A4_9A_E5_B8_83_E9_87_8C_E6_96_AF_E7_9A_84_E6_8A_AB_E9_A2_A8_Coat_of_Brandobaris/avatar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"434\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>布蘭多布里斯的披風 Coat of Brandobaris &nbsp;@Item[d4k9RN1cUqVDn9gk]{布蘭多布里斯的披風 Coat of Brandobaris}</p>\n<p>需同調；</p>\n<p>原先是一件背部繡有布蘭多布里斯徽記的深藍色披風，是那位以亂偷東西聞名【賊手 茶火】的代表裝備，在茶火不幹冒險者退休回家後將其改為毯子珍惜的使用著，當寶貝孫女決定遠行時，委託女兒將其縫入孫女的外套中，但卻忘記教導孫女要如何使用，便目送孫女出了遠門。</p>\n<p>當穿著這件披風(外套)並將布蘭多布里斯的徽記露出來時，穿戴者可以無視周遭環境使用一個動作進行躲藏，當成功等級大於周遭生物的被動感知時，便能獲得隱形狀態。直到下一次會發出聲音的動作、攻擊或是法術，此外移動不會令穿戴著現形，且隱形時下一次的攻擊會帶優勢。</p>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/008_-__E9_AD_94_E6_B3_95_E7_89_A9_E5_93_81/001_-__E5_B8_83_E8_98_AD_E5_A4_9A_E5_B8_83_E9_87_8C_E6_96_AF_E7_9A_84_E6_8A_AB_E9_A2_A8_Coat_of_Brandobaris/avatar.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":1,"handout-archived":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_optp5abt0i","path":"魔法物品","color":"#a3488b"}}}
{"name":"GM 第二章:劫掠者營地","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_5u9o8q371jg","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/龍后寶山(完結)#/CF_SEP/GM Note","color":"#ff0000"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"}},"_id":"4ipdPHo1MqAH1yF1","pages":[{"name":"GM 第二章:劫掠者營地","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">第二章:劫掠者營地(1)</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">關於營地</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">三個團體的集合:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">最右 - 龍巫教教徒營地 &amp; 被綁住的【萊奧森 厄蘭澤】</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">中下 - 黑旗營地(南方傭兵) ； 左下 - 血色落日營地(北方傭兵)</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">中上 - 交誼臨時酒吧/餐廳 ； 左上 - 俘虜與看管者</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"> </p>"},"_id":"Go9xnQxutKcDQ1oW","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"GM 第二章:劫掠者營地","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">第二章:劫掠者營地(1)</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">關於營地</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">三個團體的集合:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">最右 - 龍巫教教徒營地 &amp; 被綁住的【萊奧森 厄蘭澤】</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">中下 - 黑旗營地(南方傭兵) ； 左下 - 血色落日營地(北方傭兵)</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">中上 - 交誼臨時酒吧/餐廳 ； 左上 - 俘虜與看管者</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"> </p>"},"_id":"dvclfHMJigvCHvrC","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats"