{"name":"TiaCh2_06","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_91qsq1mthnr","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章#/CF_SEP/TiaCh2_GM用","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"TiaCh2_06","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>這是個狹長且往下傾斜的走道，任何進行DC17調查的PC都能發現在走道的中央兩側有個小通道可以跳到下方約30呎的樓梯上(通往區域10、11)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>在走道入口約15尺的地方有個絆線鉤，隊伍的第一人能用<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC22察覺判定</span>發現它；</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>當陷阱被啟動，走道頂端的馬賽克太陽就會打開，一顆直徑7呎的骸骨球就會從中浮起，並往下滾直到撞到區域7的牆壁。@JournalEntry[gqyMO3fTPpNCU3zm]{骸骨球陷阱}</p>"},"_id":"74zd98yrxvgZDMrO","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241273750,"modifiedTime":1685241273750,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"4jIvHUveY5FT6fHR"}
