{"_id":"7nnRPQuLe7eZGrXL","name":"Knight 騎士","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Illusions/Knight.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"237\" height=\"381\" /></p>\n<p>一名人類騎士與四名隨從</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_bs5gcp3h004","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Illusion","color":"#6b5988"}}}
{"_id":"7uF6PzJOyXILBA1P","name":"鐵手教團(Order of Gauntlet)","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":2,"handout-archived":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_489mkekfcw5","path":"世界觀#/CF_SEP/2.五大組織","color":"#003780"}},"pages":[{"name":"Figure: 鐵手教團(Order of Gauntlet)","type":"image","src":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/004_-__E4_B8_96_E7_95_8C_E8_A7_80/001_-_2._E4_BA_94_E5_A4_A7_E7_B5_84_E7_B9_94/002_-__E9_90_B5_E6_89_8B_E6_95_99_E5_9C_98_28Order_of_Gauntlet_29/avatar.png","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"_id":"kzTVQpP7KzYtphNV","image":{},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"鐵手教團(Order of Gauntlet)","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/004_-__E4_B8_96_E7_95_8C_E8_A7_80/001_-_2._E4_BA_94_E5_A4_A7_E7_B5_84_E7_B9_94/002_-__E9_90_B5_E6_89_8B_E6_95_99_E5_9C_98_28Order_of_Gauntlet_29/avatar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"348\" /></p>\n<p>鐵手教團，是以有紀律且毫不猶豫的粉碎邪惡聞名；教團內對於邪惡的偽裝與伎倆十分的了解，因此一旦教團的成員發現了邪惡，他們便會在它做出任何行動前將其徹底剷除。</p>\n<p>也因為理解邪惡的種子時常淺藏在陰影之下，在這主要以聖騎士、武僧與牧師組成的教團中，除了禱告外，成員們也時常手持利劍前往危險的地牢、黑暗的洞窟、與破敗的遺跡中親自與邪惡對抗。</p>\n<p>教團相信所有有的生靈最後皆會以自己的意志走向正道；並且一個人的信仰、朋友與自身便是最強大的武器；並以為世界帶來光明、驅除黑暗為宗旨。</p>"},"_id":"c5D29VSSFnI6C7hc","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"Figure: 鐵手教團(Order of Gauntlet)","type":"image","src":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/004_-__E4_B8_96_E7_95_8C_E8_A7_80/001_-_2._E4_BA_94_E5_A4_A7_E7_B5_84_E7_B9_94/002_-__E9_90_B5_E6_89_8B_E6_95_99_E5_9C_98_28Order_of_Gauntlet_29/avatar.png","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"_id":"ppiNuYUERugszce9","image":{},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"鐵手教團(Order of Gauntlet)","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/004_-__E4_B8_96_E7_95_8C_E8_A7_80/001_-_2._E4_BA_94_E5_A4_A7_E7_B5_84_E7_B9_94/002_-__E9_90_B5_E6_89_8B_E6_95_99_E5_9C_98_28Order_of_Gauntlet_29/avatar.png\" alt width=\"200\" height=\"348\" /></p>\n<p>鐵手教團，是以有紀律且毫不猶豫的粉碎邪惡聞名；教團內對於邪惡的偽裝與伎倆十分的了解，因此一旦教團的成員發現了邪惡，他們便會在它做出任何行動前將其徹底剷除。</p>\n<p>也因為理解邪惡的種子時常淺藏在陰影之下，在這主要以聖騎士、武僧與牧師組成的教團中，除了禱告外，成員們也時常手持利劍前往危險的地牢、黑暗的洞窟、與破敗的遺跡中親自與邪惡對抗。</p>\n<p>教團相信所有有的生靈最後皆會以自己的意志走向正道；並且一個人的信仰、朋友與自身便是最強大的武器；並以為世界帶來光明、驅除黑暗為宗旨。</p>"},"_id":"ahJ9TeV9dfUBO1vo","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241405190,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
