{"name":"晨曦成年禮","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_9hlpd7uaw1","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/龍后寶山(完結)#/CF_SEP/文件","color":"#38b765"}},"_id":"7yXmBQ1VxjsaGg1W","pages":[{"name":"晨曦成年禮","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">哈穆斯將右手放在卡米爾頭上後，像是宣示一樣的開始朗誦起了禱詞；</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">「我，哈穆斯在此以盧克 晨曦首席弟子之名，見證你這趟遠行的成果並承認你的成長，卡米爾 晨曦，從此日開始賜予你『晨曦』之名，願你能不受種族、性別、年齡的影響，昂首行走於大陸上。」</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">..</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">..</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">「另外....這個東西先借給你吧」，哈穆斯邊說著邊把日倫佛珠從脖子取下戴到卡米爾身上，接著說道「盡管你對氣的掌握度已經提升了很多，但在龍巫教的幹部前這樣還不夠，我們會幫你們把沃拉格哈曼薩拖住的，龍巫教就交給你們啦，可靠的後輩們!」</p>"},"_id":"Hbyzq5GlY9dxCWdK","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"晨曦成年禮","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">哈穆斯將右手放在卡米爾頭上後，像是宣示一樣的開始朗誦起了禱詞；</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">「我，哈穆斯在此以盧克 晨曦首席弟子之名，見證你這趟遠行的成果並承認你的成長，卡米爾 晨曦，從此日開始賜予你『晨曦』之名，願你能不受種族、性別、年齡的影響，昂首行走於大陸上。」</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">..</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">..</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">「另外....這個東西先借給你吧」，哈穆斯邊說著邊把日倫佛珠從脖子取下戴到卡米爾身上，接著說道「盡管你對氣的掌握度已經提升了很多，但在龍巫教的幹部前這樣還不夠，我們會幫你們把沃拉格哈曼薩拖住的，龍巫教就交給你們啦，可靠的後輩們!」</p>"},"_id":"xqDo9LXoDI3Oh3WN","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241483471,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
{"_id":"8HssU31cbJb2rknC","name":"命運 The Fates","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Fates.png\" width=\"184\" height=\"247\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>重新編織那現實的紡線...命運就在我手中。</em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>你可以避開或消除一個事件，就如同它從未發生過；你可以在抽出卡牌的瞬間或死亡之前的任一時間使用這張卡片的能力。</p>\n</section>\n<p> </p>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Fates.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_hz58kjjjx1","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Many Things","color":"#6b5988"}}}
{"name":"#[CF_tempEntity]","flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_473kql26j91","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第一章","color":"#c56a20","name":"第一章","children":[],"folderPath":["temp_o7blercjfag"],"fontColor":"#FFFFFF","icon":null,"sorting":"a","contents":["dC8pepe2OWoFODJN","dlxgZ5MrueD1vSus"],"version":"2.5.7"}},"pages":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241264668,"modifiedTime":1685241265682,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"_id":"8piT0fIog4RvqiVm"}
{"name":"TiaCh2_03","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_91qsq1mthnr","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章#/CF_SEP/TiaCh2_GM用","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"TiaCh2_03","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>遺跡的內部非常陰暗，寬廣的走道兩側站著六座身穿長袍的雕像，中央散落著骨骸與破舊的武器，雕像的兜帽裡面一片黑暗，看不清楚模樣。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p>『禁忌的知識非凡人所能碰觸，遠..遠..離....<span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">黑....暗..............</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">』</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<section class=\"secret gm-secret\">\n<h1>雕像陷阱</h1>\n<p>當PC走過走道的一半時，四周雕像的頭部伴隨者石磨般的聲音開始動了起來，原本只是直直看著前方的雕像現在全部都將臉轉向了PC。</p>\n<p>看往兜帽裡黑暗的玩家，需要進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC15 感知豁免</span>；</p>\n<p>成功的PC重獲身體的控制權不受其影響。</p>\n<p>失敗的PC會不受控的盯著那無盡的黑暗一個回合並且聽見雕像對他的低語，進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC15 智力豁免</span>；</p>\n<p>成功的PC會陷入維持10分鐘的@RollTable[2wPtPG968A7b1zLE]{短暫性瘋狂} ，當瘋狂結束後理解到禁忌知識的PC在接下來24小時內獲得智力檢定的優勢。</p>\n<p>失敗的PC無法理解雕像的話語，無影響。</p>\n</section>"},"_id":"qaakpPpPAA7HRsM0","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241272740,"modifiedTime":1685241272740,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"8xRTzUxTStLh5BU9"}
{"name":"TiaCh2_22","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_91qsq1mthnr","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章#/CF_SEP/TiaCh2_GM用","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"TiaCh2_22","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>六座蛇人雕像坐落在這間房間的兩側，張開的嘴裡散發著綠色的光芒。房間的最深處是個雕刻成巨大張嘴眼鏡蛇的祭壇，而在躺祭壇上面滿身是血一動也不動的矮人，就是你們這次尋找的目標，白之瓦拉姆，當然那是如果他還活者的話。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>##所有撤退的蜥蜴人/蛇人都會到這間房間</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p>1.若是PC在進來這裡前有在蛇人/蜥蜴人面前提到要尋找瓦拉姆，蛇人祭司就會拿著龍之匕首抵著瓦拉姆的喉嚨來作要脅。她不在乎也不知道為何PC會要找這個矮人</p>\n<p>2.若祭司不知道PC們正在尋找瓦拉姆，她會用<span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">瓦拉姆在事前答應要給蛇人們一大筆財富來與PC們做談判 (瓦拉姆對蛇人的承諾是假的，想藉此換到自由) 。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">能夠一路殺到這裡來的PC們對蛇人們來說是極大的威脅，為了不被滅族，祭司會盡可能地說服PC離開；不論是情況1或2，她都會答應放過矮人只要PC們不要在傷害她的族人，若是談判破裂她會對PC內看起來像隊長的角色施放@Item[iFCkPglJRNNsGvcQ]{暗示術 Suggestion}，試圖強迫PC接受。法術失敗 &amp; 談判也破裂的話，祭司會直接砍死瓦拉姆並帶領她的族人對玩家發動總攻擊。@Item[iYcaoimPW11bb0SM]{龍牙匕首}</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>西方的寶物庫暗門需要<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC15調查檢定/DC18察覺檢定</span>來發現其中兩座雕像的底座有機關可以打開暗門，分別通往戶外 &amp; 寶物庫。</p>\n<p>寶物庫 : 800gp、100pp、 3顆200gp 綠寶石，一串由10顆珍珠組成的項鍊(每顆100gp)，@Item[M2T9GEt3VnYGO3Mi]{浮空術 Levitate}、@Item[GBQxV2Bq2l4aBr2J]{緩慢術 Slow}卷軸</p>\n<p> </p>"},"_id":"JtdFsCz9wkbPAW49","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241279147,"modifiedTime":1685241279147,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"93gAgVck07zEEoiy"}
