{"name":"托杜爾的卷軸","flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"shop","purchasing":"confirm","items":[{"name":"法術卷軸: 維生術 Spare the Dying","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-sky-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>維生術 Spare the Dying (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個生命值為 0 的活體生物，使該生物的傷勢立刻穩定下來。該法術對不死生物和構裝生物無效。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 277","quantity":5,"weight":0,"price":"20 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"50 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"rqp7IXvPNki9X0jl","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 光亮術 Light","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-sky-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>光亮術 Light (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個尺寸在任意方向上都不超過 10 尺的物件。在法術終止前，物件將在其 20 尺半徑範圍內發出明亮光照，並在其外 20 尺範圍發出微光光照。光的顏色由你決定，該物件被不透明的東西完全遮蓋時，其光照被遮擋。如果你再次施展該法術，或者使用一個動作解散該法術，則該法術終止。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>如果你指定敵對生物所持握或著裝的一個物件作為目標，則該生物必須進行一次敏捷豁免以嘗試擺脫該法術的效應。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 255","quantity":5,"weight":0,"price":"10 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"20 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"8Veat31b0L6Nz3nu","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 睡眠術 Sleep","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-magenta-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>睡眠術 Sleep (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>該法術使一些生物陷入魔法造成的沉睡中。擲一次 5d8；其結果為受該法術影響生物的生命值總數。你指定施法距離一點，該點周圍 20 尺區域內的生物以剩餘生命值由小至大的順序受法術影響（生效時忽略昏迷生物）。</p>\n<p>計算受法術影響生物時，從剩餘生命值最低的生物開始逐個計算。每個受術生物均陷入昏迷，直至法術終止。睡眠者受到傷害也會驚醒，又或者由其他人以一個動作將其搖醒或打醒。法術擲骰的生命值總數減去一個受術生物的生命值後，餘數再用以計算生命值稍高者是否受法術影響。生物剩餘生命值，必須小於等於該餘數法術才能成功影響該生物。</p>\n<p>不死生物以及免疫魅惑效果的生物不受該法術影響。</p>\n<hr />\n<p>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，法術的擲骰就增加 2d8。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 276","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":20,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":90,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["5d8",""]],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"h9GvQIQIf7g3e4v8","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 魔法飛彈 Magic Missile","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/fire-arrows-magenta-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>魔法飛彈 Magic Missile (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>你創造三枚由魔法力場形成的閃光飛鏢，並讓每發飛鏢命中施法距離內你能看見的指定生物。每發飛鏢對目標造成 1d4+1 的力場傷害。所有飛鏢同將時命中目標，而你還可以指定它們擊中同一個目標或是分別擊中幾個目標。</p>\n<p><strong>Higher Levels.&nbsp;</strong>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，該法術就會多製造出一支飛鏢。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 257","quantity":3,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + 1","force"]],"versatile":"1d4+1"},"formula":"1d4+1","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"XMHwdVF8ck0XBpQy","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 偵察魔法 Detect Magic","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-blue-2.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>偵察魔法 Detect Magic (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>在法術時效內你可以偵察位處自己30 尺內的魔法。如果你因此偵察到魔法，你可以用你的動作窺看範圍內的可視生物或可視物體的微弱魔法氣場，看得見的話你得知該魔法的派系。<br /><br />此法術能穿透大部分障礙物，但1 尺磚石、1 寸金屬、薄鉛、或3 尺木材都足以擋住它。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 231","quantity":3,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"lXnCXM3vKan2a2xX","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 治癒真言 Healing Word","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-jade-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>治癒真言 Healing Word (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>你指定施法距離內一個你能看見的生物並恢復期生命值，恢復量等於 1d4+你的施法關鍵能力值調整值。該法術對構裝體和不死生物無效。<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，治療量就增加 1d4 點。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 250","quantity":2,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"nwVJNBJIWP6Ly9Fv","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 飛行術 Fly","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/link-spirit-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>飛行術 Fly (Level 3)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個自願生物，並使該目標在法術持續時間內獲得 60 尺的飛行速度。法術終止時，如果目標仍在空中則隨即墜落。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>使用 4 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 3 環高一環，就可以額外再指定一個生物作為法術目標。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 13 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 15<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +7.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 13 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 243","quantity":0,"weight":0,"price":"0 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":7,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":3,"cost":"0 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":600000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"wCvp5g7snigqq9xY","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 次級復原術 Lesser Restoration","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-sky-1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>次級復原術 Lesser Restoration (Level 2)</h3><hr/><h2><strong>次級復原術 Lesser Restoration</strong></h2>\n<p>你觸碰一個生物，並終止正影響它的一項疾病或一種狀態。該狀態可以是目盲，耳聾，麻痺或中毒其一。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 12 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 12 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 255","quantity":2,"weight":0,"price":"200 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":2,"cost":"200 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"hgFcdVn5n1jQKYhZ","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 魔法武器 Magic Weapon","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/enchant-blue-2.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>魔法武器 Magic Weapon (Level 2)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一件非魔法武器，並使其在法術持續時間內成為魔法武器。該武器進行攻擊檢定和傷害擲骰時具有+1 加值。</p>\n<p>使用 4 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，加值增加至+2。使用 6 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，加值增加至+3。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 12 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 12 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 257","quantity":2,"weight":0,"price":"200 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":2,"cost":"200 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"LCcfESdyv7hlHKBD","hide":false,"lock":false},{"name":"法術卷軸: 傳訊術 Message","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/yellow_01.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>傳訊術 Message (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你用手指指向施法距離內的一個生物並低聲說出一段信息。該目標（且只有該目標）會聽到這段信息並可以用只有你能聽見的低語回覆你。</p>\n<p>你可以隔著固態物件施展該法術，但你必須熟悉法術目標並知曉其就在屏障後方。魔法的沉默，1 尺厚的石頭，1 寸厚的普通金屬，一片薄鉛片，或者 3 尺厚的木料都可以阻擋該法術。該法術不需要直線傳遞信息，它可以自由地轉過拐角或穿過孔洞。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":5,"weight":0,"price":"10 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"20 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"ZTqR8Qpe8GKPi06k","hide":false,"lock":false},{"_id":"k4Mw9r883DD5DH8d","name":"重力偵測石 Stone of Gravity detection","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/stone/boulder-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>雖然看起來如同一般的石頭，但它可以增測到附近的重力的影響，只要將重力偵測石從空中放開，若是落到地上就代表現在周遭有重力，反之則是沒有。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"100 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"cost":"100 gp"},"effects":[],"folder":"Mr08h8Ts9lUBggMF","sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{},"hide":false,"lock":false}],"sell":1,"buy":0.5,"scrollPos":"{\".shop-items\":0,\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0}","_lasttab":"items","shoptype":"行商人","location":"巴里斯凱爾橋","ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":{"notes":""}},"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"shop"},"cf":{"id":"temp_jqc4xf7p0uo","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"托杜爾的卷軸","type":"image","src":"modules/monks-enhanced-journal/assets/shop.png","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"_id":"JQXASg0kAAV05pt4","image":{},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"shop","purchasing":"confirm","items":[{"name":"法術卷軸: 維生術 Spare the Dying","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-sky-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"20 gp","cost":"50 gp","quantity":5}},"_id":"rqp7IXvPNki9X0jl","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>維生術 Spare the Dying (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個生命值為 0 的活體生物，使該生物的傷勢立刻穩定下來。該法術對不死生物和構裝生物無效。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 277","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"20 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"50 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 光亮術 Light","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-sky-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"10 gp","cost":"20 gp","quantity":5}},"_id":"8Veat31b0L6Nz3nu","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>光亮術 Light (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個尺寸在任意方向上都不超過 10 尺的物件。在法術終止前，物件將在其 20 尺半徑範圍內發出明亮光照，並在其外 20 尺範圍發出微光光照。光的顏色由你決定，該物件被不透明的東西完全遮蓋時，其光照被遮擋。如果你再次施展該法術，或者使用一個動作解散該法術，則該法術終止。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>如果你指定敵對生物所持握或著裝的一個物件作為目標，則該生物必須進行一次敏捷豁免以嘗試擺脫該法術的效應。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 255","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"10 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"20 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 睡眠術 Sleep","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-magenta-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"50 gp","cost":"50 gp","quantity":1}},"_id":"h9GvQIQIf7g3e4v8","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>睡眠術 Sleep (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>該法術使一些生物陷入魔法造成的沉睡中。擲一次 5d8；其結果為受該法術影響生物的生命值總數。你指定施法距離一點，該點周圍 20 尺區域內的生物以剩餘生命值由小至大的順序受法術影響（生效時忽略昏迷生物）。</p>\n<p>計算受法術影響生物時，從剩餘生命值最低的生物開始逐個計算。每個受術生物均陷入昏迷，直至法術終止。睡眠者受到傷害也會驚醒，又或者由其他人以一個動作將其搖醒或打醒。法術擲骰的生命值總數減去一個受術生物的生命值後，餘數再用以計算生命值稍高者是否受法術影響。生物剩餘生命值，必須小於等於該餘數法術才能成功影響該生物。</p>\n<p>不死生物以及免疫魅惑效果的生物不受該法術影響。</p>\n<hr />\n<p>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，法術的擲骰就增加 2d8。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 276","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":20,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":90,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["5d8",""]],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 魔法飛彈 Magic Missile","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/fire-arrows-magenta-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"50 gp","cost":"50 gp","quantity":3}},"_id":"XMHwdVF8ck0XBpQy","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>魔法飛彈 Magic Missile (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>你創造三枚由魔法力場形成的閃光飛鏢，並讓每發飛鏢命中施法距離內你能看見的指定生物。每發飛鏢對目標造成 1d4+1 的力場傷害。所有飛鏢同將時命中目標，而你還可以指定它們擊中同一個目標或是分別擊中幾個目標。</p>\n<p><strong>Higher Levels.&nbsp;</strong>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，該法術就會多製造出一支飛鏢。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 257","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + 1","force"]],"versatile":"1d4+1"},"formula":"1d4+1","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 偵察魔法 Detect Magic","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/light-blue-2.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"50 gp","cost":"50 gp","quantity":3}},"_id":"lXnCXM3vKan2a2xX","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>偵察魔法 Detect Magic (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>在法術時效內你可以偵察位處自己30 尺內的魔法。如果你因此偵察到魔法，你可以用你的動作窺看範圍內的可視生物或可視物體的微弱魔法氣場，看得見的話你得知該魔法的派系。<br /><br />此法術能穿透大部分障礙物，但1 尺磚石、1 寸金屬、薄鉛、或3 尺木材都足以擋住它。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 231","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 治癒真言 Healing Word","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-jade-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2900000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"50 gp","cost":"50 gp","quantity":2}},"_id":"nwVJNBJIWP6Ly9Fv","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>治癒真言 Healing Word (Level 1)</h3><hr/><p>你指定施法距離內一個你能看見的生物並恢復期生命值，恢復量等於 1d4+你的施法關鍵能力值調整值。該法術對構裝體和不死生物無效。<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>使用 2 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 1 環高一環，治療量就增加 1d4 點。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 11 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 11 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 250","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"50 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":1,"cost":"50 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 飛行術 Fly","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/link-spirit-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":600000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"0 gp","cost":"0 gp","quantity":0}},"_id":"wCvp5g7snigqq9xY","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>飛行術 Fly (Level 3)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一個自願生物，並使該目標在法術持續時間內獲得 60 尺的飛行速度。法術終止時，如果目標仍在空中則隨即墜落。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>使用 4 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，你使用的法術位每比 3 環高一環，就可以額外再指定一個生物作為法術目標。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 13 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 15<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +7.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 13 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 243","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"0 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":7,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":3,"cost":"0 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 次級復原術 Lesser Restoration","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/heal-sky-1.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"200 gp","cost":"200 gp","quantity":2}},"_id":"hgFcdVn5n1jQKYhZ","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>次級復原術 Lesser Restoration (Level 2)</h3><hr/><h2><strong>次級復原術 Lesser Restoration</strong></h2>\n<p>你觸碰一個生物，並終止正影響它的一項疾病或一種狀態。該狀態可以是目盲，耳聾，麻痺或中毒其一。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 12 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 12 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 255","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"200 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":2,"cost":"200 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 魔法武器 Magic Weapon","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/enchant-blue-2.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"200 gp","cost":"200 gp","quantity":2}},"_id":"LCcfESdyv7hlHKBD","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>魔法武器 Magic Weapon (Level 2)</h3><hr/><p>你觸碰一件非魔法武器，並使其在法術持續時間內成為魔法武器。該武器進行攻擊檢定和傷害擲骰時具有+1 加值。</p>\n<p>使用 4 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，加值增加至+2。使用 6 環或更高法術位施展該法術時，加值增加至+3。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 12 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 12 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 257","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"200 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":2,"cost":"200 gp"}},{"name":"法術卷軸: 傳訊術 Message","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/skills/yellow_01.jpg","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":500000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"10 gp","cost":"20 gp","quantity":5}},"_id":"ZTqR8Qpe8GKPi06k","hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>傳訊術 Message (Level 0)</h3><hr/><p>你用手指指向施法距離內的一個生物並低聲說出一段信息。該目標（且只有該目標）會聽到這段信息並可以用只有你能聽見的低語回覆你。</p>\n<p>你可以隔著固態物件施展該法術，但你必須熟悉法術目標並知曉其就在屏障後方。魔法的沉默，1 尺厚的石頭，1 寸厚的普通金屬，一片薄鉛片，或者 3 尺厚的木料都可以阻擋該法術。該法術不需要直線傳遞信息，它可以自由地轉過拐角或穿過孔洞。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 10 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"10 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":0,"cost":"20 gp"}},{"_id":"k4Mw9r883DD5DH8d","name":"重力偵測石 Stone of Gravity detection","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/stone/boulder-grey.webp","effects":[],"folder":"Mr08h8Ts9lUBggMF","sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"lock":false,"hide":false,"price":"100 gp","cost":"100 gp","quantity":1}},"hide":false,"lock":false,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>雖然看起來如同一般的石頭，但它可以增測到附近的重力的影響，只要將重力偵測石從空中放開，若是落到地上就代表現在周遭有重力，反之則是沒有。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":"100 gp","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"cost":"100 gp"}}],"sell":1,"buy":0.5,"scrollPos":"{\".shop-items\":0,\".tab.description .tab-inner\":0}","_l