{"_id":"AQKHySbpuwPY4Jmm","name":"製作藥水與卷軸","content":"<h2>製作治癒藥水 (XGE p.129)</h2>\n<p>條件:</p>\n<p>製作者需要擁有藥草工具熟練並且花費金錢與時間，就能製作治癒藥水，詳細花費如下；</p>\n<table style=\"width: 88.4083%; height: 194px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%; text-align: center;\">藥水種類</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">時間</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">金錢</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%;\">@Item[eRZSjgEmMkVyAPeW]{治療藥水 potion of Healing}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">1天</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">25 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%;\">@Item[XOhpDh5HzdyR4Y9f]{高等治癒藥水 Potion of Greater Healing}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">10天</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">100 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%;\">@Item[x9LSQdf9NAbR1GP1]{強效治癒藥水 Potion of Superior Healing}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">30天</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">300 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%;\">@Item[0av0XUkD3nlf5zER]{極效治癒藥水 Potion of Supreme Healing}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">40天</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">800 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 39.9537%;\">@Item[AUN005HQ6MWe6zec]{神效治癒藥水 Potion of Godlike Healing}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8756%; text-align: center;\">100天</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.3184%; text-align: center;\">3000 gp</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>製作法術卷軸(XGE p.133)</h2>\n<p>條件:</p>\n<p>製作者需要擁有奧術技能熟練。並且提供紙張(羊皮紙)、法術需求的材料、金錢與時間就能製作一張法術卷軸；</p>\n<p>製作出來的法術卷軸，必須是在製作者法術列表上並且有準備的法術，詳細金錢與時間花費如下；</p>\n<table style=\"width: 86.9692%; height: 267px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">法術等級</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">時間</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">金錢</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">戲法</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">1天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">15 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">一環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">1天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">25 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">二環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">3天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">250 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">三環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">10天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">500 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">四環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">20天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">2500 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">五環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">40天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">5000 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 36.1032%; height: 18px;\">六環</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 23.3524%; height: 18px;\">80天</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 39.6848%; height: 18px;\">15000 gp</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td st