{"_id":"BVltZQTBDBGm6cqL","name":"第二章:凡達林(下)","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_kka09q4ou8","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/凡戴爾的失落礦坑(待續)","color":"#24c7f0"}},"pages":[{"name":"第二章:凡達林(下)","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">2020.03.28</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">1372 DR&nbsp; 3/12&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">半身人奧爾頓與地侏齊爾托因為不同的理由也來到了凡達林；並在石丘旅店中與瓦瑞斯、戴倫、黑斯肯相遇；雖然第一映像十分詭異，但奧爾頓與齊爾托同意了全身青草味的瓦瑞斯的邀請，加入了隊伍一同討伐紅標幫。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">冒險者們從卡普告知的密道潛入後，遭遇了諾斯異怪，在與牠之間的談判破裂後，冒險者們靠著人數優勢，輕鬆地解決了牠，並從牠的寶貝箱子中搜刮到了被稱為利爪的魔法長劍、一張卷軸以及一大筆的財富。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">而後，冒險者繼續前進，悄悄的探聽了前面道路的兩間房間，並發現到皆有敵人；冒險者們決定在樓梯中放火，並打算一口氣解決兩間房內的全部敵人，另他們沒有想到的是，其中一間房的敵人繞到了冒險者們的後背並展開攻擊，令冒險者們陷入兩面夾擊的狀態；在用盡全力的掙扎後，抵不過兩面夾擊劣勢的冒險者們就這樣..永遠地消失在幽暗的地窖中。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>"},"_id":"zI4PyVNPbibW8M2V","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"第二章:凡達林(下)","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">2020.03.28</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">1372 DR  3/12 </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">半身人奧爾頓與地侏齊爾托因為不同的理由也來到了凡達林；並在石丘旅店中與瓦瑞斯、戴倫、黑斯肯相遇；雖然第一映像十分詭異，但奧爾頓與齊爾托同意了全身青草味的瓦瑞斯的邀請，加入了隊伍一同討伐紅標幫。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">冒險者們從卡普告知的密道潛入後，遭遇了諾斯異怪，在與牠之間的談判破裂後，冒險者們靠著人數優勢，輕鬆地解決了牠，並從牠的寶貝箱子中搜刮到了被稱為利爪的魔法長劍、一張卷軸以及一大筆的財富。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\">而後，冒險者繼續前進，悄悄的探聽了前面道路的兩間房間，並發現到皆有敵人；冒險者們決定在樓梯中放火，並打算一口氣解決兩間房內的全部敵人，另他們沒有想到的是，其中一間房的敵人繞到了冒險者們的後背並展開攻擊，令冒險者們陷入兩面夾擊的狀態；在用盡全力的掙扎後，抵不過兩面夾擊劣勢的冒險者們就這樣..永遠地消失在幽暗的地窖中。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:9px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:18px\"> </p>"},"_id":"QzAujR9FszeMz575","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241472278,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
