{"_id":"Ft1a7qTgAPWLjHON","name":"愚者 Fool","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Fool.png\" width=\"180\" height=\"248\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>前進，不論前方是什麼樣的障礙。</em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>你失去10,000經驗值，捨棄這張卡牌，並再從牌組中抽取一張卡牌，將這二次抽牌視作你宣告抽牌數量的其中一次。若失去這些經驗值將導致你降低一個等級，則你改為失去足以讓你剛好維持當前等級的經驗值。</p>\n</section>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Fool.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_hz58kjjjx1","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Many Things","color":"#6b5988"}}}
