{"_id":"Iliwpyu5ckOsGN0Z","name":"#[CF_tempEntity]","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_djcfje5ejq6","path":"世界觀#/CF_SEP/1.都市與城鎮#/CF_SEP/無冬城(NeverWinter)","color":"#003780","name":"無冬城(NeverWinter)","children":[],"folderPath":["temp_7hc79aev5yf","temp_ja5a00blif8"],"fontColor":"#FFFFFF","icon":null,"sorting":"m","contents":["h1JLuuXgGUVH2wm8","R3qz8X6j9lHuvgVi","WU2bimMNVVwjU29R","WaeqnhQpsXXmHvQT","FUoKUgjh8FNXd3da"],"version":"2.5.7"}},"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"pages":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241400873,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
{"name":"龍巫教","flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"base","scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}","_lasttab":"description"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"base"},"cf":{"id":"temp_o7blercjfag","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"龍巫教","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h3>龍語者<span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">(WyrmSpeaker)</span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>腥紅之塞維林_Severin the Red</li>\n<li>蒼藍之加爾文_Galven the Blue</li>\n<li>翠綠之內洛維_Neronvain the Green</li>\n<li>漆黑之瑞茲米爾_Rezmir the Black (X)</li>\n<li>幻白之瓦拉姆_Varram the White (X)</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>龍魂(DragonSoul)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li> 弗魯蘭 蒙達斯_Frulam Mondath</li>\n<li>塔莉絲_Tails</li>\n<li>歐塞爾斯坦_Othelstan</li>\n<li>喬根 帕爾_Jorgen Pawl</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>龍牙(DragonFang)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>蘭德卓薩 青怒_Langderosa Cyanwrath</li>\n<li>麥卡苟斯 諾克維爾_Micargos Noquviir</li>\n<li data-target=\"Aja9AvmIUDSRJriT-name\" data-placeholder=\"角色名\" data-maxlength=\"40\">德拉莫瑞 灰生_Dralmorrer Borngray</li>\n<li>伊斯坎德爾_Iskander</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>龍巫教階級</p>\n<ol>\n<li>龍語者(WyrmSpeaker)</li>\n<li>龍魂(DragonSoul)</li>\n<li>龍牙(DragonFang)</li>\n<li>龍翼(DragonWing)</li>\n<li>龍爪(DragonClaw)</li>\n</ol>"},"_id":"U9Uozd36Dxc6u7ny","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"base","scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}","_lasttab":"description"}}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241260543,"modifiedTime":1685241260543,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"IoC4dJ7GoRgvCbYH"}
{"name":"TiaCh2_16","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_91qsq1mthnr","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章#/CF_SEP/TiaCh2_GM用","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"TiaCh2_16","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>蛇人冥想室</p>\n<p>在東邊的牆邊放著兩座蛇人的雕像，石製的雕像鑲嵌著紅寶石作為眼睛，有那麼一瞬間似乎覺得眼睛正放出紅色的光芒，<span style=\"color:#191813;font-family:Signika;font-size:13px\">在它們的面前有兩具黑色的鎧甲以單膝跪下的姿勢跪坐在雕像前。</span></p>\n<p>DC15宗教檢定能判斷出這兩座雕像分別是蛇人的神祇，<span style=\"color:#191813;font-family:Signika;font-size:13px\">梅爾紹克 Merrshaulk(左) 與 賽斯 Sseth(右)；</span></p>\n<p>當PC靠近雕像，幾隻蛇突然開始從雕像的嘴裡跑了出來，一隻、兩隻、十隻、二十隻，PC看到彷彿洪水般的蛇從雕像的嘴裡湧出，掉到了地面上。</p>\n<p>接著，地面上的蛇沒有展開攻擊反而是爬向了蹲踞的雕像前的兩具鎧甲，你們就這樣看著蛇群們鑽入鎧甲之中，接著兩座原本蹲下的鎧甲就這樣站了起來，拔出他的長劍，朝PC攻擊了過來。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>#雕像的眼睛是價值1000gp/顆的紅寶石，使用工具可以將其無損的取下@JournalEntry[h2mlPW4oNcu6V6D2]{蛇人石像}</p>\n<p> </p>"},"_id":"RcbAWVSOjLExoF9D","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241277135,"modifiedTime":1685241277135,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"IoCxwF1NJmE23TnN"}
