{"name":"蛇人的寶物庫","flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"loot","purchasing":"confirm","items":[{"_id":"7T8jyL098Sm8WOMb","name":"綠寶石 Emeralds","type":"loot","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-princess-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":3,"weight":0,"price":"200","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true},"effects":[],"folder":"zFXB56nMNAKJVmRC","sort":100000,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Bu5g7bm5BPXmhQ8p"}},"from":""},{"_id":"qjiBLgtRHY7MgH7T","name":"珍珠項鍊 Perl Neckless","type":"tool","img":"icons/commodities/gems/pearls-white.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一串由10顆珍珠組成的項鍊</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 154","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":"1000","attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"toolType":"","baseItem":"","ability":"cha","chatFlavor":"","proficient":1,"bonus":"","damage":{"parts":[]},"critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null}},"effects":[],"folder":"zFXB56nMNAKJVmRC","sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"onUseMacroName":"","effectActivation":false},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lYiVqZs1HU3SuoFh"},"favtab":{"isFavorite":false}},"from":""},{"name":"法術卷軸: 浮空術 Levitate","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/wind-grasp-magenta-2.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>浮空術 Levitate (Level 2)</h3><hr/><p>你所選的射程內的一名生物或物體垂直升起最多20 尺，浮在空中直到時效結束。此法術能舉起最重500 磅的目標。非自願的生物只要成功通過體質豁免則不受影響。目標只能靠推拉觸及內的物體或表面，例如牆或天花，才能好像攀爬一樣移動。你可以在你的回合中改變目標的高度最多20 尺。如果目標是你自己，你可以用你的移動力去升降。否則，你需要用你的動作移動目標，目標也必需保持在射程之內。<br /><br />當法術終結時，如果目標依然在漂浮，他會輕柔地著地。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 12 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 13<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +5.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 12 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 255","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":120,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":5,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"scroll","attributes":{"spelldc":10},"level":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":700000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_id":"O9TrnTGtWV9lBS9g","from":""},{"name":"法術卷軸: 緩慢術 Slow","type":"consumable","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/systems/dnd5e/assets/icons/spells/fog-magenta-2.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spell scroll bears the words of a single spell, written in a mystical cipher. If the spell is on your class's spell list, you can read the scroll and cast its spell without providing any material components. Otherwise, the scroll is unintelligible. Casting the spell by reading the scroll requires the spell's normal casting time. Once the spell is cast, the words on the scroll fade, and it crumbles to dust. If the casting is interrupted, the scroll is not lost.</p><hr/><h3>緩慢術 Slow (Level 3)</h3><hr/><p>你在施法距離內一處 40 尺立方區域內指定至多六個生物並扭曲其周圍的時間流。每個目標都要進行一次感知豁免，豁免失敗則受到該法術影響直至法術終止。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>受術生物的速度減半，而其 AC 和敏捷豁免都具有－2 減值，且不能執行反應。該生物在其回合內可以執行一個動作或一個附贈動作，但不能在一回合內同時執行以上兩者。不論該生物擁有何種能力或魔法物品，它在其回合內只能發動一次近戰或遠程攻擊。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>如果該生物嘗試施展一個施法時間為 1 動作的法術，則需擲一次 d20。如果結果是 11 或更高，則該生物的法術直至其下一回合才會生效，且該生物必須在此時再使用一個動作來完成法術。如果它做不到則它的法術就此浪費掉。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>受術生物在每個其自己回合結束時可以再進行一次該感知豁免，豁免成功則終止其身上的該法術效應。</p><hr/><h3>Scroll Details</h3><hr/>\n<p>If the spell is on your class's spell list but of a higher level than you can normally cast, you must make a DC 13 ability check using your spellcasting ability to determine whether you cast it successfully. On a failed check, the spell disappears from the scroll with no other effect.</p>\n<p>The level of the spell on the scroll determines the spell's saving throw DC and attack bonus, as well as the scroll's rarity.</p>\n<p><strong>Save DC</strong>: 15<br><strong>Attack Bonus</strong>: +7.</p>\n<p>A wizard spell on a spell scroll can be copied just as spells in spellbooks can be copied. When a spell is copied from a spell scroll, the copier must succeed on a DC 13 Intelligence (Arcana) check. If the check succeeds, the spell is successfully copied. Whether the check succeeds or fails, the spell scroll is destroyed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 277","quantity":1,"