{"name":"TiaCh2_04","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"},"cf":{"id":"temp_91qsq1mthnr","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章#/CF_SEP/TiaCh2_GM用","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"TiaCh2_04","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>地板上以磁磚描繪一幅騎士對抗奇美拉的馬賽克畫像，進入房間的PC可以進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC14的察覺檢定</span>來辦定是否有注意到馬賽克奇美拉的緩緩移動；</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>5號 : 往上的通道門口被人用粉筆大大的寫著SAFE</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>6號 : 往下的長走廊是個斜坡，在頂端有個馬賽克太陽的圓型石磚(<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC24察覺 / DC18調查</span>得知這是一個陷阱)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>12號 : 往右的門有些變形的從門框上突起，門上繪製者一群巫師圍繞水池的畫像，其中一個壯碩的男巫師正舉著手像是召喚著什麼一般。若是將門打開，堆積在上的落石會一口氣掉落，所有在門範圍10尺內的生物進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC18敏捷豁免</span>，失敗會受到8d6的鈍擊傷害，成功半傷 。</p>\n<p> </p>"},"_id":"QabEyZImbaiIr2WO","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241273084,"modifiedTime":1685241273084,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"LIFwKkal0YNmiGsn"}
{"name":"寢室的寶物","flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"loot","scrollPos":"{\".loot-items\":0}","actors":["qutepihdqE5YX1DF","E9Xx40segpndKajg","vEbtCC3psQOxHIrO","FX8HmEidYqHtSOso","T4u2wPUumVIU50iS","70rR4uA9VFUXKhng"],"items":[],"purchasing":"locked","currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0}},"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"loot"},"cf":{"id":"temp_jqc4xf7p0uo","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"寢室的寶物","type":"image","src":"modules/monks-enhanced-journal/assets/loot.png","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"_id":"Ezx4kA5XbLpFRkJk","image":{},"text":{"format":1},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"loot","scrollPos":"{\".loot-items\":0}","actors":["qutepihdqE5YX1DF","E9Xx40segpndKajg","vEbtCC3psQOxHIrO","FX8HmEidYqHtSOso","T4u2wPUumVIU50iS","70rR4uA9VFUXKhng"],"items":[],"purchasing":"locked","currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0}}}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241268636,"modifiedTime":1685241268636,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"LVVlMLZwJBdgdn07"}
{"_id":"LWn0pIDH8hFu4d5e","name":"Orge 食人魔","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Illusions/Ogre.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"379\" /></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_bs5gcp3h004","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Illusion","color":"#6b5988"}}}
{"name":"某冒險者的手記","flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_4dwst4r0zoi","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/來自故人的委託","color":"#3ab6a1"}},"pages":[{"name":"某冒險者的手記","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h1>False Hydra </h1>\n<h4>(以下簡稱F.H.)</h4>\n<p>-</p>\n<p>-</p>\n<p>因為F.H.的歌唱特性，要對付它十分不容易，在與經過多次的嘗試後，我們統整出了以下幾個弱點；</p>\n<p>1.只要透過鏡子的倒影，就算是受到歌唱的影響也能觀察到F.H.的存在</p>\n<p>2.減少頭的數量能夠令歌曲的效果減弱</p>\n<p>3. 與一般的Hydra不同並沒有對火焰的弱點，但再生能力較低</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>在我與夥伴的旅行過程中，曾經遇到過這麼一個恐怖的對手；記憶被隨意篡改的恐懼，比站在成年紅龍的面前還令人發顫，即使事情已經過去了這麼多年我仍時常在想，是不是有某個夥伴被我們給遺忘了。</p>\n<p>我在此留下這些紀錄，希望能對未來的冒險者們有所幫助。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>以利亞 班克斯 1307.12.04</p>"},"_id":"9eqhf9WFPzRpFXVJ","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241539939,"modifiedTime":1685241539939,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"LcWJBM6D7DOV5MYF"}
{"_id":"Ll510wDCGttW8gDr","name":"NPC GM Note","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"gm-notes":{"notes":"<p>遭遇:</p>\n<p>1</p>\n<p>@Actor[WFdbTxvaSQinjrYU]{枯針怪 Needle Blight}X2</p>\n<p>@Actor[SGeh6l5DFrzSvopA]{枯藤怪 Vine Blight}X1</p>\n<hr />\n<p>2</p>"},"cf":{"id":"temp_kic6spue1d","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/萊安娜與羅曼的大冒險","color":"#de9f17"}},"pages":[{"name":"NPC GM Note","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>潛行森林</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>艾摩斯 312歲 費爾柏格 藥草師/3等德魯伊 ；</p>\n<p>沉默寡言，住在潛行森林邊緣，身高8.3呎(2.5m)，身邊有一隻叫做嫩芽的雄鹿陪伴。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>碧 Bi 700歲 內睿德；綠寶石湖泊的守護者。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>海拉 Haelra 卓爾</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p>米拉巴</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>米拉巴大商人克拉克家族 Clark family (精靈)</p>\n<p>女當家 / 考特妮 克拉克 Courtney Clark</p>\n<p>管家/ 肖恩 克拉克 Sean Clark </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>觀星之塔魔法師:</p>\n<p>巴恩 Baern 矮人</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>綿羊法師 / 菲瑟爾 光亮 Finethir Shinebright</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>烏鴉人力派遣公司 :</p>\n<p>雷吉 懷特 人類 山羊鬍</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>任務管理人:</p>\n<p>諾亞·比伯 半身人</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p>大哥布林</p>\n<p>柯基(Corg)_22歲</p>\n<p>索格(Sog)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>哥布林</p>\n<p>德魯普(Droop)_10歲</p>\n<p>鼻涕(Snot)_6歲</p>\n<p>蛙臉(Frogface)_9歲</p>\n<p>蹦蹦(BoneBone)_9歲</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:line-through\">鼻屎(Booger)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>食人魔</p>\n<p>石頭(Rock)</p>"},"_id":"yBbYtR8UKB2fLpVQ","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"NPC GM Note","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>潛行森林</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>艾摩斯 312歲 費爾柏格 藥草師/3等德魯伊 ；</p>\n<p>沉默寡言，住在潛行森林邊緣，身高8.3呎(2.5m)，身邊有一隻叫做嫩芽的雄鹿陪伴。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>碧 Bi 700歲 內睿德；綠寶石湖泊的守護者。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>海拉 Haelra 卓爾</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p>米拉巴</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>米拉巴大商人克拉克家族 Clark family (精靈)</p>\n<p>女當家 / 考特妮 克拉克 Courtney Clark</p>\n<p>小少爺/ 提姆 克拉克 Tim Clark</p>\n<p>管家/ 肖恩 克拉克 Sean Clark </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>觀星之塔魔法師:</p>\n<p>巴恩 Baern 矮人</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>綿羊法師 / 菲瑟爾 光亮 Finethir Shinebright</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>烏鴉人