{"_id":"OpyYdrBvjkpKHIFP","name":"長休/看哨規則","content":"<p>當隊伍進行長休時，依照周遭環境狀況進行判定，看哨時分為【上半哨】與【下半哨】兩班，每哨4小時。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>1.當冒險者待在城鎮、旅店等等安全地點，長休無須任何檢定，也不用守夜、看哨。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2.當冒險者待在野外/森林等等潛伏危機地點，長休時每一班哨點都需進行【1次】1d20檢定；每次長休最多觸發1次事件。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>3.當冒險者待在地牢、敵人領土等等危險地點，長休時每一班哨點都須進行【2次】1d20檢定；每次長休最多觸發2次事件。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 99.1549%; height: 102px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 99.2898%; height: 18px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\">長休判定</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.1364%; height: 18px; text-align: center;\">骰值</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.1534%; height: 18px; text-align: center;\">結果</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.1364%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.1534%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">特殊戰鬥(危)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.1364%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2~3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.1534%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">隨機事件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.1364%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4~19</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.1534%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">平靜的休息時光</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.1364%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.1534%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">特殊事件(好)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>#當冒險者在長休/看哨中途進行了戰鬥後，解決事件的冒險者在長休結束後會獲得一階段的@JournalEntry[HamUWSIGpVKNidC7]{力竭 Exhaustion}，持續到下一次無打擾的長休為止。</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ga8fwsospb","path":"規則書#/CF_SEP/房規","color":"#003780"}}}
