{"name":"骸骨球陷阱","flags":{"_document-sheet-registrar":{"type":"base"},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"base","attributes":{"age":{"value":""},"size":{"value":""},"government":{"value":""},"alignment":{"value":""},"faction":{"value":""},"inhabitants":{"value":""},"districts":{"value":""},"agricultural":{"value":""},"cultural":{"value":""},"educational":{"value":""},"indistrial":{"value":""},"mercantile":{"value":""},"military":{"value":""}},"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}","style":{"color":"","img":{"value":"","meta":{}},"sizing":"repeat"}},"cf":{"id":"temp_jqc4xf7p0uo","path":"提亞馬特的覺醒#/CF_SEP/第二章","color":"#c56a20"}},"pages":[{"name":"骸骨球陷阱","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\">骸骨球來啦~~ 快跑起來!! </span></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">(一個由無數骷髏組合而成的巨大球球，正滿心期待地把路上的東西全部碾碎)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">規則:</span></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">1.全員骰先攻決定行動順序，骸骨球的順序固定最後</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">2.每一回合可以選擇以下兩種移動方式；</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align:left\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">一般的跑 : </span>移動10呎</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">死命的跑 : </span>進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">運動檢定</span>每次成功可以移動10呎，DC從10開始每次成功+5；但若是失敗就會原地滑倒，下回合移動-5呎。請自行評斷體能決定是否要繼續。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">3.每回合骸骨球的移動速度為20呎，只會直線滾動</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">4.被骸骨球輾過去的話要進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC17的敏捷豁免</span>，失敗會受到4d8<span style=\"font-size:11pt\">穿刺</span>+4d8<span style=\"font-size:11pt\">鈍擊</span>傷害，並且被球上面的骸骨抓住跟著球一起往下滾。成功半傷並且閃開骸骨們的手手。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">5.如果被抓住了，每個回合可以進行<span style=\"background-color:#f1c40f\">DC17運動 /特技檢定</span>來掙脫</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">6.當球撞到牆壁粉碎時還在球上面的人會受到</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:18.6667px\">4d6</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">穿刺</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:18.6667px\">+4d6</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">鈍擊</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:18.6667px\">傷害</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>"},"_id":"UaPLLCSD1jjbDdoU","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"monks-enhanced-journal":{"type":"base","attributes":{"age":{"value":""},"size":{"value":""},"government":{"value":""},"alignment":{"value":""},"faction":{"value":""},"inhabitants":{"value":""},"districts":{"value":""},"agricultural":{"value":""},"cultural":{"value":""},"educational":{"value":""},"indistrial":{"value":""},"mercantile":{"value":""},"military":{"value":""}},"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}","style":{"color":"","img":{"value":"","meta":{}},"sizing":"repeat"}}}}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685241269351,"modifiedTime":1685241269351,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_id":"WFwkooa7g1xyzNz0"}
{"name":"#[CF_tempEntity]","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_x1vv7qoxw4h","path":"商店#/CF_SEP/魔法商店 女巫與貓","color":"#0f61e6","name":"魔法商店 女巫與貓","children":[],"folderPath":["temp_ftt9d4ksi8f"],"fontColor":"#FFFFFF","icon":null,"sorting":"a","contents":["EQAL3TFrlyEEdJBM","f8v9S5Gg45ZY4nYU","fApYmM056T6ufIBE","BgQoDyijfL56e2o5","J2iJc47gcVKoKn9b"],"version":"2.5.7"}},"_id":"WPh2JM30zwEKqyCF","ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"pages":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241259049,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
{"_id":"WU2bimMNVVwjU29R","name":"海灘上的利維坦","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":1,"handout-archived":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_djcfje5ejq6","path":"世界觀#/CF_SEP/1.都市與城鎮#/CF_SEP/無冬城(NeverWinter)","color":"#003780"}},"pages":[{"name":"海灘上的利維坦","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">海灘上的利維坦(Beached Leviathan)位於無冬城西北方黑湖區(Blacklake District)的海岸邊；</p><p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">就如同他的名子這間酒館/旅店是個用一艘名維利維坦的海盜船改裝而成；只是在船尾上開了個小門，再把整艘船拖上堤防，就這樣熱鬧歡騰的海灘上的利維坦就此在無冬城開張。</p><p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">這裡的老闆是利維坦號原本的船長，曾經的海盜頭子哈瑞格(Hagar)，身為人類的他有著蠟黃色的皮膚、粗壯的身體、以及一隻走路咚咚作響的木腿；在旅店的大廳裡時常能聽到他咚咚作響的木腿以及他與酒客們豪邁笑聲。</p><p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">作為無冬城中最受歡迎的旅店之一，利維坦裡面每天都非常的熱鬧，裡面有著來自世界各地剛航行至無冬城的商人、剛從探險中歸來的冒險者、或是只是來小酌一杯的水手與市民；只要花上幾個銅幣，不論是男女老少，在利維坦內都能找到一些樂趣。</p><p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">作為最受歡迎的酒館之一，利維坦理所當然的也是冒險者們尋求委託、交換情報的絕佳地點；許多的委託人都會在此張貼告示，尋求著厲害的冒險者。</p>"},"_id":"YOfIGBhKJ5nYXE8r","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"海灘上的利維坦","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p style=\"color:rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">海灘上的利維坦(Beached Leviathan)位於無冬城西北方黑湖區(Blacklake District)的海岸邊；</p><p style=\"color:rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">就如同他的名子這間酒館/旅店是個用一艘名維利維坦的海盜船改裝而成；只是在船尾上開了個小門，再把整艘船拖上堤防，就這樣熱鬧歡騰的海灘上的利維坦就此在無冬城開張。</p><p style=\"color:rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">這裡的老闆是利維坦號原本的船長，曾經的海盜頭子哈瑞格(Hagar)，身為人類的他有著蠟黃色的皮膚、粗壯的身體、以及一隻走路咚咚作響的木腿；在旅店的大廳裡時常能聽到他咚咚作響的木腿以及他與酒客們豪邁笑聲。</p><p style=\"color:rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">作為無冬城中最受歡迎的旅店之一，利維坦裡面每天都非常的熱鬧，裡面有著來自世界各地剛航行至無冬城的商人、剛從探險中歸來的冒險者、或是只是來小酌一杯的水手與市民；只要花上幾個銅幣，不論是男女老少，在利維坦內都能找到一些樂趣。</p><p style=\"color:rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">作為最受歡迎的酒館之一，利維坦理所當然的也是冒險者們尋求委託、交換情報的絕佳地點；許多的委託人都會在此張貼告示，尋求著厲害的冒險者。</p>"},"_id":"HeIvOVnljN1QyRoE","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241399190,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
