{"name":"柏德之門(Baldur's Gate)","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":2,"handout-archived":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_ja5a00blif8","path":"世界觀#/CF_SEP/1.都市與城鎮","color":"#003780"}},"content":"<p>柏德之門是個繁忙的貿易中心，南北的貨物經由貿易公路(The Trade Way)的馬車與寶劍海(Sea of Sword)的船隻過來；東邊的科米爾(Cormyr)和桑比亞(Sembia)的各種貨物也會經由沖薩河到這裡；城市坐落在河口邊一個突出的懸崖上，向下俯瞰著絕佳的天然海港。</p><p>柏德之門主要分為三個不同的城區；上城區(Upper City)是最富有最具影響力人們的居住地，城市的集市也位在這一區域。環繞港口的下城區(Lower City)是城市中大部分商人居住及展開事業的地點。最後則是外城區(Outer City)大多數的工人都住在那髒亂壅擠的空間中。</p><div><br></div>","img":"","_id":"gwxSr8DrhGXhoS6c"}
{"_id":"gz9hcsyfyv6gV62m","name":"曆法與時間  Time in the Realms","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_7hc79aev5yf","path":"世界觀","color":"#003780"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"}},"pages":[{"name":"曆法與時間  Time in the Realms","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h1><strong>遺忘國度的時間 Time in the Realms</strong></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>儘管各地民族與歷史有數種紀錄時間流逝的方法，但費倫大陸大多數採行『<strong>Calendar of Harptos(哈普托斯曆法)</strong>』。幾乎所有種族、語言與文化都能辨別該曆法。</p>\n<p>該曆法將托瑞爾大陸一年分12個月，每月為30日，其中每10日稱為一週。在這些日子之外，又另外加上了5個特別的年度節日，總計365日為一年。每4年一次，於閏年會額外加入一日『Shieldmeet(盾會節)』。</p>\n<table style=\"height: 273px; width: 490px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">月份</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">俗名</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 15px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 15px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 15px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Hammer</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 15px; text-align: center;\">深冬之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 332px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"3\">仲冬節 Midwinter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Aluriak</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">冬爪之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Ches</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">暮爪之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Tarsakh</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">風爪之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"3\">綠草節&nbsp;Greengrass</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Mirtul</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">融雪之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Kythorn</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">花期之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Flamerule</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">夏潮之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"3\">仲夏節&nbsp;Midsummer</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"3\">*盾會日 Shieldmeet(四年一次)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">Eleasias</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; height: 14px; text-align: center;\">烈日之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 17px;\">9</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 17px;\">Eleint</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; text-align: center; height: 17px;\">枯萎之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 17px;\" colspan=\"3\">豐收節&nbsp;High harvest tide</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">10</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">Marpenoth</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">落葉之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">11</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">腐葉之月</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\" colspan=\"3\">月之祭典 The feast of the Moon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px; width: 35px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">12</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 147px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">Nightal</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.25em 0px; width: 150px; text-align: center; height: 14px;\">歲末之月</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>特殊節日</strong></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>雖然每個國家、信仰與文化都有自己的節慶，但<strong>Harptos</strong>仍記載了5個最主要的節慶，用來象徵四季的變化。而這5日也被大多數的民眾所慶賀。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>仲冬節 Midwinter</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>在Heartlands(中心大陸)被稱為High Festival of Winter(冬之祭典)，在北境與Moonsea(月之海)等寒冷地帶則稱為Deadwinter Day(亡冬之日)，代表寒冷的冬季即將死去、最糟糕的時節已經過去。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>綠草節 Greengrass</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>象徵春季的開始，慶典會將新收割的花卉(若是外頭仍未到花期則通常是培養在溫室中)獻給神明與自然。並祈求接下來一年農作順利。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>仲夏節 Midsummer</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>盛夏正中的節日，通常伴隨著盛大的宴會、酒會、婚禮、與各種狂歡慶典。</li>\n<li>在仲夏節的夜晚發生的暴風雨，被視為凶兆，或者上天不贊成此日成婚的新人。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>盾會日 Shieldmeet</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>四年一次的大節慶，緊接在仲夏節後舉行，是個暢所欲言、萬物更新的節日。統治階級將大開議堂廣邀名人志士建言、道路與建築將重新修葺、冤仇在此日重新協商調解。同時也是許多大型競賽或技藝測驗舉行的日子，許多宗教信仰亦會選在這天向世人彰顯自己的信條。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>　　*1472年正好是盾會日發生之年。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"},"_id":"Ki6KU2UUjOzpHEHU","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"曆法與時間  Time in the Realms","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h1><strong>遺忘國度的時間 Time in the Realms</strong></h1>\n<p> </p>\n<p>儘管各地民族與歷史有數種紀錄時間流逝的方法，但費倫大陸大多數採行『<strong>Calendar of Harptos(哈普托斯曆法)</strong>』。幾乎所有種族、語言與文化都能辨別該曆法。</p>\n<p>該曆法將托瑞爾大陸一年分12個月，每月為30日，其中每10日稱為一週。在這些日子之外，又另外加上了5個特別的年度節日，總計365日為一年。每4年一次，於閏年會額外加入一日『Shieldmeet(盾會節)』。</p>\n<table style=\"height:273px;width:490px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);marg