{"_id":"jLa3YF2HT6TtIqYO","name":"蛇髮女妖 Euryale","content":"<p><img src=\"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Euryale.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"188\" height=\"246\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>她的目光詛咒著你。</p>\n<hr />\n<p>你所有的豁免骰得到劣勢。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>這張卡片的效果只能由以下方式解除：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>牧師的@Item[A2pauIkG927FlGp5]{神聖干預}</li>\n<li>@JournalEntry[wek93lpR0befvQj1]{命運}</li>\n<li>@Item[seOAvDIoyf2Sa0SR]{高等復原術}</li>\n</ul>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5fbe632f22e31d07aa87f83c/Magic%20Deck/Deck%20of%20Many%20Things/The_Euryale.png","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"gm-notes":{"notes":""},"cf":{"id":"temp_hz58kjjjx1","path":"魔法物品#/CF_SEP/Deck of Many Things","color":"#6b5988"}}}
{"name":"GM 第七章:狩獵旅社","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_5u9o8q371jg","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/龍后寶山(完結)#/CF_SEP/GM Note","color":"#ff0000"},"_document-sheet-registrar":{},"monks-enhanced-journal":{"scrollPos":"{\".description\":0}"}},"_id":"jVT6rHHeqqFqk9ZY","pages":[{"name":"GM 第七章:狩獵旅社","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p> </p>\n<p>(1)在這片樹林的周圍還有另外兩座傳送門的石陣；</p>\n<p>分別在其石柱上刻上了「哀鳴之不安沼澤」、「雪域」、「紅日」</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(5)從大廳門口的兩個精靈盔甲間穿越需要進行DC15 CON豁免/1d12冷凍傷害</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(6)客廳/會客室東南角落的牆壁上掛有傳送掛毯，可將穿越的人傳送至5里外的隨機地點(通常是在鹿、野豬的附近)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(15)在被褥間內有一 面有著五道顏色的旗幟(黑、藍、綠、紅、白)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>"},"_id":"0OizRoNPEFne9hZr","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"GM 第七章:狩獵旅社","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p> </p>\n<p>(1)在這片樹林的周圍還有另外兩座傳送門的石陣；</p>\n<p>分別在其石柱上刻上了「哀鳴之不安沼澤」、「雪域」、「紅日」</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(5)從大廳門口的兩個精靈盔甲間穿越需要進行DC15 CON豁免/1d12冷凍傷害</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(6)客廳/會客室東南角落的牆壁上掛有傳送掛毯，可將穿越的人傳送至5里外的隨機地點(通常是在鹿、野豬的附近)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>(15)在被褥間內有一 面有著五道顏色的旗幟(黑、藍、綠、紅、白)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>"},"_id":"Lh3OHktD5zKbG4s7","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241520113,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
{"_id":"jeVFK26R9hFnIbGP","name":"神秘遺跡牆上的碑文","folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_kic6spue1d","path":"歷史的痕跡#/CF_SEP/萊安娜與羅曼的大冒險","color":"#de9f17"},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.lzjMeSrkaPqynTMe"}},"pages":[{"name":"神秘遺跡牆上的碑文","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color: #191813;\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">LuBa</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color: #191813;\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">The spells on these locks are all the same.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Though each possesses a unique name.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Count on your answer to unlock the way.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">But use the wrong key to your dismay.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>"},"_id":"d3nutfmwBoKdxAbL","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"name":"神秘遺跡牆上的碑文","type":"text","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color:#191813\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">LuBa</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" style=\"color:#191813\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">The spells on these locks are all the same.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Though each possesses a unique name.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">Count on your answer to unlock the way.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"><span class=\"polyglot-journal\" title=\"龍語\" data-language=\"draconic\">But use the wrong key to your dismay.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"> </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813\"> </p>"},"_id":"Dbuci8H9GPVihDLZ","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"1.6.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1685241526436,"lastModifiedBy":"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI"}}
{"name":"咒法瘟疫 Spellplague","permission":{"default":0,"ZunkTzckD5EJj8XI":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_7hc79aev5yf","path":"世界觀","color":"#003780"}},"content":"<h1><strong>咒法瘟疫 Spellplague</strong></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>1385DR冬末春初，費倫全境爆發了一場非自然的魔法災難。魔網(Weave)因不明原因失控，原本充斥於奧術領域的秩序被混亂的狂野魔法取代，全大陸各地都發生地震、海嘯、生物異變，同時以光耀之海(The Shining Sea)南方為中心，詭異的藍色火焰急速擴散並席捲了數個文明城市。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>咒印 Spellscars</strong></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>大多數受到咒法瘟疫影響的生物會因無法承受變異而死亡，但若有倖存者會在身上留下咒法影響的印記。咒印的型態並無固定規律，少數帶有咒印者會以某種方式顯現奧術的才能/特性，但獲得能力同時也往往伴隨著某種缺陷。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><strong>晶鱗病 Crystalscale</strong></h3>\n<p>咒印的其中一種型態，患者皮膚表面會出現類似透明晶礦般的構造，並隨著時間演進擴散。被晶體覆蓋之四肢會變得僵硬，以至於患者在疫病後期幾乎只能臥床。晶鱗病具致死性，當皮膚完成一定程度變異後，結晶將會轉往臟器，直到患者喪生。</p>\n<p>目前未有遭證實的醫治方式，訪間流傳某種以石灰和銀粉製作的藥方能抑制晶體的擴散，也有藥師認為切除患部能延長患者性命。部分神殿則試圖透過祈禱與神術來治癒疾病。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","_id":"jghnJq53rMCQ6RIN"}
